snippet.title: [All Time Favorite Game #21] Best VGM 1430 - Bioshock - Welcome to Rapture
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Xbox 360 / PS3 / PC
Bioshock (2007)
Welcome to Rapture
Gary Schyman
